data.title: Pickle - Your AI body double in zoom calls
data.description: Pickle lets your AI body double join zoom calls instead of you. It lip-syncs to your voice, so you don't have to turn on your camera. Create your Pickle and make your zoom call easy.

How it works

To make your Pickle, simply record a 5-minute video of yourself

and wait 24 hours for AI to train your appearance.

![Image 66](https://framerusercontent.com/images/e5jdBkbDjHW732PgWQR4a5t3Kws.jpg)

Load

Your AI body double, will show up in seconds.

![Image 67](https://framerusercontent.com/images/L4HWym73RgRYlLZ6H07aphq1uac.png)

![Image 68](https://framerusercontent.com/images/Vc1Q7ku60VT1VaSD32Qg2lvQ.jpg)

Switch

Select Camera as your video feed.

![Image 69](https://framerusercontent.com/images/L4HWym73RgRYlLZ6H07aphq1uac.png)

![Image 70](https://framerusercontent.com/images/BOPUeXyX98pyRjma3SacM7AOc.jpg)

Talk

Your will lip-sync to your voice in real time.

![Image 71](https://framerusercontent.com/images/L4HWym73RgRYlLZ6H07aphq1uac.png)

![Image 72](https://framerusercontent.com/images/77Wa925D7IkBRxbCk3KWKhCy0go.png)
